\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces \textbf  {System deployment and latency architecture} separating the latency-critical synchronous inference path from the asynchronous safety adaptation loop. Lightweight context confusion and fast metacognitive checks are deployed on a synchronous reverse proxy with a strict latency budget ($<$50\,ms), while hybrid judge ensemble evaluation, distributional policy synthesis, and controlled mutation operate out-of-band in an asynchronous loop, preserving runtime throughput by removing expensive adaptation components from the critical path.}}{5}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:deployment}{{2}{5}{\textbf {System deployment and latency architecture} separating the latency-critical synchronous inference path from the asynchronous safety adaptation loop. Lightweight context confusion and fast metacognitive checks are deployed on a synchronous reverse proxy with a strict latency budget ($<$50\,ms), while hybrid judge ensemble evaluation, distributional policy synthesis, and controlled mutation operate out-of-band in an asynchronous loop, preserving runtime throughput by removing expensive adaptation components from the critical path}{figure.2}{}}
