\newlabel{fig:degradation}{{3}{7}{\textbf {Defensive degradation and heterogeneous recovery flow.} When axiomatic conflict or psychological manipulation is detected, the gateway preserves synchronous API availability by routing the session to a restricted low-privilege stateless SLM sandbox with template-bound outputs and no tool or external API access, while human audit and symbolic recovery proceed asynchronously out-of-band}{figure.3}{}}
